Paging {{{2
	bat - cat alternative.  
		https://github.com/sharkdp/bat
		dnf install
		Show git diffs -d

	batextras https://github.com/eth-p/bat-extras/tree/master?tab=readme-ov-file
		batgrep, batman, batpipe, batdiff

	delta - diff alternative.  Pkg git-delta

	riff - git diff pager
		https://github.com/walles/riff

